Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer Inc., distributor
of James Bond and Rocky movies, filed for bankruptcy after
rejecting a takeover bid by  Lions Gate Entertainment Corp . and
billionaire  Carl Icahn .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Pickering at 
 jpickering@bloomberg.net  